<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.PMViewDataUtils</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>*Fetches the required data for PM View Landing page</description><name>PMViewDataUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var PMViewDataUtils = Class.create();
PMViewDataUtils.prototype = {
	getPrefferedDetailsView: function(className) {
		
		var gr = new GlideRecordSecure('pm_home_page_config');
		gr.get('table', className);
		if(gr.view) {
			return gr.getValue('view');
		} 
		return null;
	},
	getPrefferedProject: function() {
		
		var prefferedProjectId = gs.getUser().getPreference('com.snc.project_management.home_page.project');
		if(prefferedProjectId) {
			return prefferedProjectId;
		} else {
			return null;
		}
	},
	getPMDetails: function() {
		return {
			id: gs.getUserID(),
			isProjectManager: gs.hasRole('project_manager'),
			userLanguage: gs.getUser().getLanguage()
		};
	},
	getTopTaskId: function(projectId) {
		
		var topTaskId = null;
		
		if(projectId) {
			topTaskId = new PlanningConsolePreferenceValidator().getTopTaskId(projectId) || this.getPrefferedProject();
		} else {
			topTaskId = this.getPrefferedProject();
		}
		return topTaskId;
		
	},
	getProjectDetails: function(className, projectId) {
		
		var isProjectAvailable;
        var topProjectId = this.getTopTaskId(projectId);
		var topClassName = SNC.PPMConfig.getProjectTable(className);
		

        if(className && topProjectId) {
			
			var gr = new GlideRecordSecure(topClassName);
			if(gr.get(topProjectId))
				isProjectAvailable = true;
			else
				isProjectAvailable = false;
			if(gr.canRead()) {
				if(!isProjectAvailable) {
					return {
						status: 'WARNING',
						message: gs.getMessage('Project is not available in the list'),
						projectSysId: '',
						className: topClassName,
						shortDescription: '',
						createAccess: gr.canCreate(),
						prefferedDetailsView: this.getPrefferedDetailsView(topClassName)
					};
				} else {
					return {
						status: 'SUCCESS',
						message: '',
						projectSysId: gr.getValue('sys_id'),
						shortDescription: gr.getDisplayValue('short_description'),
						className: topClassName,
						createAccess: gr.canCreate(),
						prefferedDetailsView: this.getPrefferedDetailsView(topClassName)
					};
				}
			} else {
				return {
					status: 'FAILURE',
					message: gs.getMessage('Unauthorized access to the project')
				};
			}
			
        } else if(className && !topProjectId) {
			
			var gr = new GlideRecordSecure(topClassName);
			if(gr.canRead()) {
				return {
					status: 'WARNING',
					message: gs.getMessage('Project id is not available'),
					projectSysId: '',
					className: topClassName,
					shortDescription: '',
					createAccess: gr.canCreate(),
					prefferedDetailsView: this.getPrefferedDetailsView(topClassName)
				};
			} else {
				return {
					status: 'FAILURE',
					message: gs.getMessage('Unauthorized access to the project!')
				};
			}
        } else {
            return {
                status: 'FAILURE',
                message: gs.getMessage('Invalid URL Parameters!')
            };
        }
    },
	getCheckListItems: function(className, projectId) {
		
		var checklistResult = {
			checklistItems: []
		};
		
		var _projectId = this.getTopTaskId(projectId);
		var checklistItemRecords = new GlideRecordSecure('checklist_item');
		if(checklistItemRecords.canRead()) {
			if(_projectId) {
				
				checklistItemRecords.addQuery('checklist.document', _projectId);
				checklistItemRecords.orderBy('order');
				checklistItemRecords.query();
				while(checklistItemRecords.next()) {
					checklistResult.checklistItems.push({
						id: checklistItemRecords.getValue('sys_id'),
						name: checklistItemRecords.getDisplayValue('name'),
						checkListId: checklistItemRecords.getValue('checklist'),
						complete: checklistItemRecords.getDisplayValue('complete'),
						order: checklistItemRecords.getValue('order')
					});
				}
			}
			checklistResult.readAccess = true;
			checklistResult.createAccess = checklistItemRecords.canCreate();
			checklistResult.updateAccess = checklistItemRecords.canWrite();
			checklistResult.deleteAccess = checklistItemRecords.canDelete();
		} else {
			checklistResult.readAccess = false;
			checklistResult.createAccess = checklistItemRecords.canCreate();
			checklistResult.updateAccess = checklistItemRecords.canWrite();
			checklistResult.deleteAccess = checklistItemRecords.canDelete();
		}
		return checklistResult;
	},getRelatedProjects: function(className, limit, offset, term) {
		
		var totalRecordsCount = 0;
		var totalProjRecords;
		var resultantRecords = [];
		
		var defaultQuery = 'active=true';
		var query = gs.getUser().getPreference('com.snc.project_management.home_page.entity_cards.query');
		var encodedQuery = query ? query + '^short_description' + 'CONTAINS' + term : defaultQuery + '^short_description' + 'CONTAINS' + term;
		
		//Fetching Count of total projects in the user's saved filter or projs assigned to user
		totalProjRecords = new GlideAggregate(className);
		totalProjRecords.addEncodedQuery(encodedQuery);
		totalProjRecords.addAggregate('COUNT');
		totalProjRecords.setGroup(false);
		totalProjRecords.query();
		
		if(totalProjRecords.next())
			totalRecordsCount = totalProjRecords.getAggregate('COUNT');
		
		//Fetching all Projects
		totalProjRecords = new GlideRecordSecure(className);
		totalProjRecords.addEncodedQuery(encodedQuery);
		totalProjRecords.chooseWindow(offset, offset+limit);
		totalProjRecords.query();
		while(totalProjRecords.next()) {

			var proj = {
				'sys_id': totalProjRecords.getValue('sys_id'),
				'short_description': totalProjRecords.getDisplayValue('short_description'),
				'project_manager.sys_id': totalProjRecords.project_manager.getValue('sys_id')
			};
			resultantRecords.push(proj);
		}
		
		return {
			result: resultantRecords,
			total: totalRecordsCount
		};
	},
	
	type: 'PMViewDataUtils'

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="DELETE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.PMViewDataUtils</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>*Fetches the required data for PM View Landing page</description><name>PMViewDataUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var PMViewDataUtils = Class.create();
PMViewDataUtils.prototype = {
	getPrefferedDetailsView: function(className) {
		
		var gr = new GlideRecordSecure('pm_home_page_config');
		gr.get('table', className);
		if(gr.view) {
			return gr.getValue('view');
		} 
		return null;
	},
	getPrefferedProject: function() {
		
		var prefferedProjectId = gs.getUser().getPreference('com.snc.project_management.home_page.project');
		if(prefferedProjectId) {
			return prefferedProjectId;
		} else {
			return null;
		}
	},
	getPMDetails: function() {
		return {
			id: gs.getUserID(),
			isProjectManager: gs.hasRole('project_manager'),
			userLanguage: gs.getUser().getLanguage()
		};
	},
	getTopTaskId: function(projectId) {
		
		var topTaskId = null;
		
		if(projectId) {
			topTaskId = new PlanningConsolePreferenceValidator().getTopTaskId(projectId) || this.getPrefferedProject();
		} else {
			topTaskId = this.getPrefferedProject();
		}
		return topTaskId;
		
	},
	getProjectDetails: function(className, projectId) {
		
		var isProjectAvailable;
        var topProjectId = this.getTopTaskId(projectId);
		var topClassName = SNC.PPMConfig.getProjectTable(className);
		
		gs.addInfoMessage(topProjectId);
		gs.addInfoMessage(topClassName);
		

        if(className && topProjectId) {
			
			var gr = new GlideRecordSecure(topClassName);
			if(gr.get(topProjectId))
				isProjectAvailable = true;
			else
				isProjectAvailable = false;
			if(gr.canRead()) {
				if(!isProjectAvailable) {
					return {
						status: 'WARNING',
						message: gs.getMessage('Project is not available in the list'),
						projectSysId: '',
						className: topClassName,
						shortDescription: '',
						createAccess: gr.canCreate(),
						prefferedDetailsView: this.getPrefferedDetailsView(topClassName)
					};
				} else {
					return {
						status: 'SUCCESS',
						message: '',
						projectSysId: gr.getValue('sys_id'),
						shortDescription: gr.getDisplayValue('short_description'),
						className: topClassName,
						createAccess: gr.canCreate(),
						prefferedDetailsView: this.getPrefferedDetailsView(topClassName)
					};
				}
			} else {
				return {
					status: 'FAILURE',
					message: gs.getMessage('Unauthorized access to the project')
				};
			}
			
        } else if(className && !topProjectId) {
			
			var gr = new GlideRecordSecure(topClassName);
			if(gr.canRead()) {
				return {
					status: 'WARNING',
					message: gs.getMessage('Project id is not available'),
					projectSysId: '',
					className: topClassName,
					shortDescription: '',
					createAccess: gr.canCreate(),
					prefferedDetailsView: this.getPrefferedDetailsView(topClassName)
				};
			} else {
				return {
					status: 'FAILURE',
					message: gs.getMessage('Unauthorized access to the project!')
				};
			}
        } else {
            return {
                status: 'FAILURE',
                message: gs.getMessage('Invalid URL Parameters!')
            };
        }
    },
	getCheckListItems: function(className, projectId) {
		
		var checklistResult = {
			checklistItems: []
		};
		
		var _projectId = this.getTopTaskId(projectId);
		var checklistItemRecords = new GlideRecordSecure('checklist_item');
		if(checklistItemRecords.canRead()) {
			if(_projectId) {
				
				checklistItemRecords.addQuery('checklist.document', _projectId);
				checklistItemRecords.orderBy('order');
				checklistItemRecords.query();
				while(checklistItemRecords.next()) {
					checklistResult.checklistItems.push({
						id: checklistItemRecords.getValue('sys_id'),
						name: checklistItemRecords.getDisplayValue('name'),
						checkListId: checklistItemRecords.getValue('checklist'),
						complete: checklistItemRecords.getDisplayValue('complete'),
						order: checklistItemRecords.getValue('order')
					});
				}
			}
			checklistResult.readAccess = true;
			checklistResult.createAccess = checklistItemRecords.canCreate();
			checklistResult.updateAccess = checklistItemRecords.canWrite();
			checklistResult.deleteAccess = checklistItemRecords.canDelete();
		} else {
			checklistResult.readAccess = false;
			checklistResult.createAccess = checklistItemRecords.canCreate();
			checklistResult.updateAccess = checklistItemRecords.canWrite();
			checklistResult.deleteAccess = checklistItemRecords.canDelete();
		}
		return checklistResult;
	},getRelatedProjects: function(className, limit, offset, term) {
		
		var totalRecordsCount = 0;
		var totalProjRecords;
		var resultantRecords = [];
		
		var defaultQuery = 'active=true';
		var query = gs.getUser().getPreference('com.snc.project_management.home_page.entity_cards.query');
		var encodedQuery = query ? query + '^short_description' + 'CONTAINS' + term : defaultQuery + '^short_description' + 'CONTAINS' + term;
		
		//Fetching Count of total projects in the user's saved filter or projs assigned to user
		totalProjRecords = new GlideAggregate(className);
		totalProjRecords.addEncodedQuery(encodedQuery);
		totalProjRecords.addAggregate('COUNT');
		totalProjRecords.setGroup(false);
		totalProjRecords.query();
		
		if(totalProjRecords.next())
			totalRecordsCount = totalProjRecords.getAggregate('COUNT');
		
		//Fetching all Projects
		totalProjRecords = new GlideRecordSecure(className);
		totalProjRecords.addEncodedQuery(encodedQuery);
		totalProjRecords.chooseWindow(offset, offset+limit);
		totalProjRecords.query();
		while(totalProjRecords.next()) {

			var proj = {
				'sys_id': totalProjRecords.getValue('sys_id'),
				'short_description': totalProjRecords.getDisplayValue('short_description'),
				'project_manager.sys_id': totalProjRecords.project_manager.getValue('sys_id')
			};
			resultantRecords.push(proj);
		}
		
		return {
			result: resultantRecords,
			total: totalRecordsCount
		};
	},
	
	type: 'PMViewDataUtils'

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>false</active><api_name>global.DemandToProjectCreationHelper</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>DemandToProjectCreationHelper</name><script><![CDATA[var DemandToProjectCreationHelper = Class.create();
DemandToProjectCreationHelper.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },

    createProject: function (sysId) {
        var sys_id = sysId, projId, projNumber, tableDisplayName;
        var demand = new GlideRecord('dmn_demand');
        demand.addQuery('sys_id', sys_id);
        demand.query();
      
        if(demand.next()) {
            sys_id = demand.getValue("sys_id");
            projId = demand.getValue("project");
            var projectTable = "pm_project";
            if(GlidePluginManager.isActive('com.snc.project_management_v3')){
                projectTable = SNC.PPMConfig.getProjectTable(demand.sys_class_name);
            }
            if(sys_id && !projId) {
                var project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
                project.initialize();
                var fields = ['short_description', 'primary_program', 'business_case', 'sys_domain', 'investment_class', 'investment_type', 'risk_of_performing', 'risk_of_not_performing', 'enablers', 'barriers', 'in_scope', 'out_of_scope', 'assumptions', 'goals', 'strategic_objectives', 'business_unit', 'department', 'impacted_business_units', 'business_applications', 'business_capabilities'];
                for(var index in fields){
                    var field = fields[index];
                    if(project.isValidField(field)){
                        project.setValue(field, demand.getValue(field));
                    }
                }
 
                project.setValue("primary_portfolio", demand.getValue("portfolio"));
                project.setValue("demand", sys_id);
                project.setValue("calculation_type", 'manual');
                var benefit = demand.financial_benefit;
                if( JSUtil.notNil(benefit) && JSUtil.notNil(benefit.getCurrencyValue())) {
                    project.benefits = benefit.getCurrencyCode() + ';' + parseFloat(benefit.getCurrencyValue());
                }
        if(new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.financial_planning_pmo')) {
          var riskDerivationFunction = ScoreFactory.riskDerivationFunction();         
          project.setValue('risk', riskDerivationFunction(demand.score_risk));
        }
                var resp = this._setProjectDatesAndDurationFromDemand(project, demand, projectTable);
                if ( resp.status == 'error' )
                    return {'sysId': null, 'number': '', 'label': 'Project', 'error': resp.message };
                
                projId = project.insert();
                if(JSUtil.nil(projId)){
                    var allErrorMessages = j2js(gs.getErrorMessages());
                    if (JSUtil.notNil(allErrorMessages) && allErrorMessages.length > 0)
                        return {'sys_id': projId, 'number': '', 'label': 'Project', 'error':allErrorMessages[0]};
                    else
                        return {'sys_id': projId, 'number': '', 'label': 'Project'};
                }
                GlideSysAttachment.copy(demand.sys_class_name, sys_id, projectTable, projId);
                projNumber = project.getValue('number');
                tableDisplayName = project.getClassDisplayValue();
                
                if(JSUtil.nil(demand.related_records))
                    demand.related_records = projId;
                else
                    demand.related_records = demand.related_records + "," + projId;
                demand.project = projId;
                demand.state = '8';
                demand.stage = 'project';
                demand.update();
                
                var projectDomain = project.sys_domain;
                var req = new GlideRecord("dmn_requirement");
                req.addQuery("parent", sys_id);
                req.query();
                while(req.next()){
                    var sourceId = req.getUniqueValue();
                    req.parent = projId;
                    req.sys_domain = projectDomain;
                    var newNumber = new NumberManager('dmn_requirement'); 
                    req.number = newNumber.getNextObjNumberPadded();
                    var reqId = req.insert();
                    GlideSysAttachment.copy('dmn_requirement', sourceId, 'dmn_requirement', reqId);
                    gs.log("Requirement created for Project " + project.number);
                }
                
                if(new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.financial_planning_pmo')){
                    this._updateFinancialRecords(sys_id, projId);
                    var budgetPlanner = new ITFMBudgetPlanner();
                    budgetPlanner.updateDemandBudgetKeysToProject(demand, projId);
                    this._copyFinancialFieldsFromDemandToProject(demand, projId, projectTable);
                }
                
                var risk = new GlideRecord("risk");
                risk.addQuery("state","!=","achieved");
                risk.addQuery("task", sys_id);
                risk.query();
                while(risk.next()){
                    risk.task = projId;
                    if (new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.program_management'))
                        risk.top_task = projId;
                    risk.sys_domain = projectDomain;
                    risk.update();
                    gs.log("Risk updated for Project " + project.number);
                }
                
                var dec = new GlideRecord("dmn_decision");
                dec.addQuery("parent", sys_id);
                dec.query();
                while(dec.next()){
                    var decSourceId = dec.getUniqueValue();
                    dec.parent = projId;
                    dec.sys_domain = projectDomain;
                    dec.setWorkflow(false);
                    var decId = dec.insert();
                    GlideSysAttachment.copy('dmn_decision', decSourceId, 'dmn_decision', decId);
                    gs.log("Decision created for Project " + project.number);
                }
                
                //Copy stories on Demand to Project
                if(new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.sdlc.agile.2.0')){
                    var projectAgileApi = new ProjectWorkbenchAgile2Apis();
                    projectAgileApi.copyStoriesFromDemandtoProject(sys_id,projId);
                }
        
        // Risk, Size and Value are copied over from demand
        project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
        if ( project.get(projId) ) {
          project.score_risk = demand.getValue("score_risk");
          project.score_size = demand.getValue("score_size");
          project.score_value = demand.getValue("score_value");
          project.score = demand.getValue('score');
          project.setWorkflow(false);
          project.update();
          project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
          project.get(projId);
        }
            }
        }
        return {'sys_id': projId, 'number': projNumber, 'label': tableDisplayName};
    },

    _setProjectDatesAndDurationFromDemand: function(project, demand, projectTable) {
        if (demand.start_date.nil())
            return;
        var resp = {"status": "success"};
        var defaultProjectScheduleId = '7aa3e10c8f70010040f82ab2f0f9234d';
        var scheduleId = SNC.PPMConfig.getProperty('com.snc.project.default_schedule', projectTable, defaultProjectScheduleId);
        var util = new ProjectTaskManagerUtil();
        var demandStart = this.getGlideDateTime(demand.getValue('start_date'), demand.getDisplayValue('start_date'), false);
        var startDateTime = util.getStartDateInternalFromSchedule(scheduleId, demandStart.getValue());
        var projectStartDateTime = new GlideDateTime();
        projectStartDateTime.setValue(startDateTime);
        project.setValue('start_date', projectStartDateTime);
        PPMDebug.log("DemandToProjectCreationHelper: projectStartDateTime -> " + projectStartDateTime.getDisplayValueInternal());
        if (!demand.requested_by.nil()) {
            var demandEnd = this.getGlideDateTime(demand.getValue('requested_by'), demand.getDisplayValue('requested_by'), true);                     
            resp = util.RecalculateDurationFromEndDatePerScheduleInternal(startDateTime, demandEnd, scheduleId);
            resp = new JSON().decode(resp);

            if ( resp.status == 'success' ) {
                project.setDisplayValue('duration', resp.duration);
            }
        }
        return resp;
    },

    getGlideDateTime: function (date, displayDate, endTime) {
      PPMDebug.log("DemandToProjectCreationHelper: getGlideDateTime - date -> " + date + " | " + displayDate);
      var dateTime = new GlideDateTime();
      if(endTime) {
        dateTime.setDisplayValue(date + " 23:59:59");  
      } else {
        dateTime.setDisplayValue(date + " 00:00:00");
      }
      PPMDebug.log("DemandToProjectCreationHelper: getGlideDateTime - dateTime -> " + dateTime.getValue() + " | " + dateTime.getDisplayValueInternal());
      return dateTime;
    },

    _updateFinancialRecords:function(demandId, projectId){
        var project = new GlideRecord('pm_project');
        project.get(projectId);

        var costPlan = new GlideRecord("cost_plan");
        costPlan.addQuery("task", demandId);
        costPlan.setValue('task', projectId);
        costPlan.setValue('top_task', projectId);
        costPlan.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        costPlan.setWorkflow(false);
        costPlan.updateMultiple();
        
        var costBreakdowns = new GlideRecord("cost_plan_breakdown");
        costBreakdowns.addQuery("task", demandId);
        costBreakdowns.setValue('task', projectId);
        costBreakdowns.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        costBreakdowns.setWorkflow(false);
        costBreakdowns.updateMultiple();
        
        var fundingRecs = new GlideRecord("project_funding");
        fundingRecs.addQuery("task", demandId);
        fundingRecs.setValue('task', projectId);
        fundingRecs.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        fundingRecs.setWorkflow(false);
        fundingRecs.updateMultiple();
        
        this.updateBenefitPlans(demandId, projectId);

        //Update estimated and budget costs
        new PlannedTaskEntityUpdater().updatePlannedTaskEstimatedCost(project);
        new PPMTaskEntityUpdater().updateBudgetCost(project);
    },

    _copyFinancialFieldsFromDemandToProject:function(demand, projectId, projectTable){
        var project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
        if ( project.get(projectId)) {
            project.discount_rate = demand.getValue("discount_rate");
            project.npv_value = demand.getValue("npv_value");
            project.irr_value = demand.getValue("irr_value");
            project.setWorkflow(false);
            project.update();
        }
    },

    updateBenefitPlans: function (demandId, projectId) {
        gs.print("Into updateBenefitPlans -> " + demandId + " | " + projectId);
        var project = new GlideRecord('pm_project');
        project.get(projectId);
        
        var benefitPlan = new GlideRecord("benefit_plan");
        benefitPlan.addQuery("task", demandId);
        benefitPlan.setValue('task', projectId);
        benefitPlan.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        benefitPlan.setWorkflow(false);
        benefitPlan.updateMultiple();

        var benefitBreakdowns = new GlideRecord("benefit_plan_breakdown");
        benefitBreakdowns.addQuery("task", demandId);
        benefitBreakdowns.setValue('task', projectId);
        benefitBreakdowns.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        benefitBreakdowns.setWorkflow(false);
        benefitBreakdowns.updateMultiple();
    },

    type: 'DemandToProjectCreationHelper'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-07-21 00:04:53</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>20e773609f702200598a5bb0657fcf25</sys_id><sys_mod_count>59</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DemandToProjectCreationHelper</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Demand Management" source="com.snc.demand_management">db6982ff6f390200d45331012e3ee4de</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_20e773609f702200598a5bb0657fcf25</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Michael.Ocasio@hhs.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-08-14 15:37:32</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_b753ce7ddbc8ef006bb976740f9619bd
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>true</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>dmn_demand</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Delete Demand</name><order>200</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[var abort = false;

if(!gs.hasRole("demand_manager")){
	
	var risk = new GlideRecord('risk');
	risk.addQuery('task', current.sys_id);
	risk.query();
	if(risk.next())
		abort = true;
	
	if(!abort){
		var decision = new GlideRecord('dmn_decision');
		decision.addQuery('parent', current.sys_id);
		decision.query();
		if(decision.next())
			abort = true;
	}
	
	if(!abort  && pm.isActive('com.snc.resource_management')){
		var rplan = new GlideRecord('resource_plan');
		rplan.addQuery('task', current.sys_id);
		rplan.query();
		if(rplan.next())
			abort = true;
	}
	
}

if(!abort)
	deleteRelatedRecords();
else{
	current.setAbortAction(true);
	gs.addErrorMessage(gs.getMessage('Demand with Risks/Decisions/Resource Plans cannot be deleted'));
}


function deleteRelatedRecords(){
	deleteRequirements();
	deleteDecisions();
	deleteResourcePlans();
	deleteDeliverables();
}


function deleteRequirements(){
	var req = new GlideRecord('dmn_requirement');
	req.addQuery('parent', current.sys_id);
	req.deleteMultiple();
}

function deleteDecisions(){
	var dec = new GlideRecord('dmn_decision');
	dec.addQuery('parent', current.sys_id);
	dec.deleteMultiple();
}

function deleteResourcePlans(){
	if(pm.isActive('com.snc.resource_management')){
		var dec = new GlideRecord('resource_plan');
		dec.addQuery('task', current.sys_id);
		dec.deleteMultiple();
	}
}

function deleteDeliverables(){
	var dec = new GlideRecord('u_deliverables');
	dec.addQuery('u_parent', current.sys_id);
	dec.deleteMultiple();
}

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_30fbd526eb031100b749215df106fe13
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access/><action_delete>true</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>dmn_demand</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Delete Demand</name><order>200</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[var abort = false;

if(!gs.hasRole("demand_manager")){
	
	var risk = new GlideRecord('risk');
	risk.addQuery('task', current.sys_id);
	risk.query();
	if(risk.next())
		abort = true;
	
	if(!abort){
		var decision = new GlideRecord('dmn_decision');
		decision.addQuery('parent', current.sys_id);
		decision.query();
		if(decision.next())
			abort = true;
	}
	
	if(!abort  && pm.isActive('com.snc.resource_management')){
		var rplan = new GlideRecord('resource_plan');
		rplan.addQuery('task', current.sys_id);
		rplan.query();
		if(rplan.next())
			abort = true;
	}
	
}

if(!abort)
	deleteRelatedRecords();
else{
	current.setAbortAction(true);
	gs.addErrorMessage(gs.getMessage('Demand with Risks/Decisions/Resource Plans cannot be deleted'));
}


function deleteRelatedRecords(){
	deleteRequirements();
	deleteDecisions();
	deleteResourcePlans();
}


function deleteRequirements(){
	var req = new GlideRecord('dmn_requirement');
	req.addQuery('parent', current.sys_id);
	req.deleteMultiple();
}

function deleteDecisions(){
	var dec = new GlideRecord('dmn_decision');
	dec.addQuery('parent', current.sys_id);
	dec.deleteMultiple();
}

function deleteResourcePlans(){
	if(pm.isActive('com.snc.resource_management')){
		var dec = new GlideRecord('resource_plan');
		dec.addQuery('task', current.sys_id);
		dec.deleteMultiple();
	}
}




]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2014-02-25 09:10:51</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>30fbd526eb031100b749215df106fe13</sys_id><sys_mod_count>27</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Delete Demand</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Demand Management" source="com.snc.demand_management">db6982ff6f390200d45331012e3ee4de</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_30fbd526eb031100b749215df106fe13</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Keith.Tucker@hhs.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-08-21 14:39:24</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=30fbd526eb031100b749215df106fe13"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.DemandToProjectCreationHelper</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>DemandToProjectCreationHelper</name><script><![CDATA[var DemandToProjectCreationHelper = Class.create();
DemandToProjectCreationHelper.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },

    createProject: function (sysId) {
        var sys_id = sysId, projId, projNumber, tableDisplayName;
        var demand = new GlideRecord('dmn_demand');
        demand.addQuery('sys_id', sys_id);
        demand.query();
      
        if(demand.next()) {
            sys_id = demand.getValue("sys_id");
            projId = demand.getValue("project");
            var projectTable = "pm_project";
            if(GlidePluginManager.isActive('com.snc.project_management_v3')){
                projectTable = SNC.PPMConfig.getProjectTable(demand.sys_class_name);
            }
            if(sys_id && !projId) {
                var project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
                project.initialize();
				//added the user defined fields u_* from the demand table to be carryover for story Project Plan 
				// STRY0020468 on 8/14/2018
                var fields = ['short_description', 'primary_program', 'business_case', 'sys_domain', 'investment_class', 'investment_type', 'risk_of_performing', 'risk_of_not_performing', 'enablers', 'barriers', 'in_scope', 'out_of_scope', 'assumptions', 'goals', 'strategic_objectives', 'business_unit', 'department', 'impacted_business_units', 'business_applications', 'business_capabilities', 'u_funding_source', 'u_it_investment', 'u_project_acronym', 'u_project_funding_type', 'u_project_level', 'u_additional_notes'];
                for(var index in fields){
                    var field = fields[index];
                    if(project.isValidField(field)){
                        project.setValue(field, demand.getValue(field));
                    }
                }
 
                project.setValue("primary_portfolio", demand.getValue("portfolio"));
                project.setValue("demand", sys_id);
                project.setValue("calculation_type", 'manual');
                var benefit = demand.financial_benefit;
                if( JSUtil.notNil(benefit) && JSUtil.notNil(benefit.getCurrencyValue())) {
                    project.benefits = benefit.getCurrencyCode() + ';' + parseFloat(benefit.getCurrencyValue());
                }
        if(new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.financial_planning_pmo')) {
          var riskDerivationFunction = ScoreFactory.riskDerivationFunction();         
          project.setValue('risk', riskDerivationFunction(demand.score_risk));
        }
                var resp = this._setProjectDatesAndDurationFromDemand(project, demand, projectTable);
                if ( resp.status == 'error' )
                    return {'sysId': null, 'number': '', 'label': 'Project', 'error': resp.message };
                
                projId = project.insert();
                if(JSUtil.nil(projId)){
                    var allErrorMessages = j2js(gs.getErrorMessages());
                    if (JSUtil.notNil(allErrorMessages) && allErrorMessages.length > 0)
                        return {'sys_id': projId, 'number': '', 'label': 'Project', 'error':allErrorMessages[0]};
                    else
                        return {'sys_id': projId, 'number': '', 'label': 'Project'};
                }
                GlideSysAttachment.copy(demand.sys_class_name, sys_id, projectTable, projId);
                projNumber = project.getValue('number');
                tableDisplayName = project.getClassDisplayValue();
                
                if(JSUtil.nil(demand.related_records))
                    demand.related_records = projId;
                else
                    demand.related_records = demand.related_records + "," + projId;
                demand.project = projId;
                demand.state = '8';
                demand.stage = 'project';
                demand.update();
                
                var projectDomain = project.sys_domain;
                var req = new GlideRecord("dmn_requirement");
                req.addQuery("parent", sys_id);
                req.query();
                while(req.next()){
                    var sourceId = req.getUniqueValue();
                    req.parent = projId;
                    req.sys_domain = projectDomain;
                    var newNumber = new NumberManager('dmn_requirement'); 
                    req.number = newNumber.getNextObjNumberPadded();
                    var reqId = req.insert();
                    GlideSysAttachment.copy('dmn_requirement', sourceId, 'dmn_requirement', reqId);
                    gs.log("Requirement created for Project " + project.number);
                }
                
                if(new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.financial_planning_pmo')){
                    this._updateFinancialRecords(sys_id, projId);
                    var budgetPlanner = new ITFMBudgetPlanner();
                    budgetPlanner.updateDemandBudgetKeysToProject(demand, projId);
                    this._copyFinancialFieldsFromDemandToProject(demand, projId, projectTable);
                }
                
                var risk = new GlideRecord("risk");
                risk.addQuery("state","!=","achieved");
                risk.addQuery("task", sys_id);
                risk.query();
                while(risk.next()){
                    risk.task = projId;
                    if (new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.program_management'))
                        risk.top_task = projId;
                    risk.sys_domain = projectDomain;
                    risk.update();
                    gs.log("Risk updated for Project " + project.number);
                }
                
                var dec = new GlideRecord("dmn_decision");
                dec.addQuery("parent", sys_id);
                dec.query();
                while(dec.next()){
                    var decSourceId = dec.getUniqueValue();
                    dec.parent = projId;
                    dec.sys_domain = projectDomain;
                    dec.setWorkflow(false);
                    var decId = dec.insert();
                    GlideSysAttachment.copy('dmn_decision', decSourceId, 'dmn_decision', decId);
                    gs.log("Decision created for Project " + project.number);
                }
                
				//Added copying the Deliverables Related List to the new project as per story Plan Project 
				// STRY0020468 on 8/14/2018
				//
				var deli = new GlideRecord("u_deliverables");
                deli.addQuery("u_parent", sys_id);
                deli.query();
                while(deli.next()){
                    var deliSourceId = deli.getUniqueValue();
                    deli.u_parent = projId;
                    deli.u_sys_domain = projectDomain;
                    var deliId = deli.insert();
                    GlideSysAttachment.copy('u_deliverables', deliSourceId, 'u_deliverables', deliId);
                    gs.log("Deliverable created for Project " + project.number);
				}

				//Copy stories on Demand to Project
                if(new GlidePluginManager().isActive('com.snc.sdlc.agile.2.0')){
                    var projectAgileApi = new ProjectWorkbenchAgile2Apis();
                    projectAgileApi.copyStoriesFromDemandtoProject(sys_id,projId);
                }
        
        // Risk, Size and Value are copied over from demand
        project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
        if ( project.get(projId) ) {
          project.score_risk = demand.getValue("score_risk");
          project.score_size = demand.getValue("score_size");
          project.score_value = demand.getValue("score_value");
          project.score = demand.getValue('score');
          project.setWorkflow(false);
          project.update();
          project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
          project.get(projId);
        }
            }
        }
        return {'sys_id': projId, 'number': projNumber, 'label': tableDisplayName};
    },

    _setProjectDatesAndDurationFromDemand: function(project, demand, projectTable) {
        if (demand.start_date.nil())
            return;
        var resp = {"status": "success"};
        var defaultProjectScheduleId = '7aa3e10c8f70010040f82ab2f0f9234d';
        var scheduleId = SNC.PPMConfig.getProperty('com.snc.project.default_schedule', projectTable, defaultProjectScheduleId);
        var util = new ProjectTaskManagerUtil();
        var demandStart = this.getGlideDateTime(demand.getValue('start_date'), demand.getDisplayValue('start_date'), false);
        var startDateTime = util.getStartDateInternalFromSchedule(scheduleId, demandStart.getValue());
        var projectStartDateTime = new GlideDateTime();
        projectStartDateTime.setValue(startDateTime);
        project.setValue('start_date', projectStartDateTime);
        PPMDebug.log("DemandToProjectCreationHelper: projectStartDateTime -> " + projectStartDateTime.getDisplayValueInternal());
        if (!demand.requested_by.nil()) {
            var demandEnd = this.getGlideDateTime(demand.getValue('requested_by'), demand.getDisplayValue('requested_by'), true);                     
            resp = util.RecalculateDurationFromEndDatePerScheduleInternal(startDateTime, demandEnd, scheduleId);
            resp = new JSON().decode(resp);

            if ( resp.status == 'success' ) {
                project.setDisplayValue('duration', resp.duration);
            }
        }
        return resp;
    },

    getGlideDateTime: function (date, displayDate, endTime) {
      PPMDebug.log("DemandToProjectCreationHelper: getGlideDateTime - date -> " + date + " | " + displayDate);
      var dateTime = new GlideDateTime();
      if(endTime) {
        dateTime.setDisplayValue(date + " 23:59:59");  
      } else {
        dateTime.setDisplayValue(date + " 00:00:00");
      }
      PPMDebug.log("DemandToProjectCreationHelper: getGlideDateTime - dateTime -> " + dateTime.getValue() + " | " + dateTime.getDisplayValueInternal());
      return dateTime;
    },

    _updateFinancialRecords:function(demandId, projectId){
        var project = new GlideRecord('pm_project');
        project.get(projectId);

        var costPlan = new GlideRecord("cost_plan");
        costPlan.addQuery("task", demandId);
        costPlan.setValue('task', projectId);
        costPlan.setValue('top_task', projectId);
        costPlan.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        costPlan.setWorkflow(false);
        costPlan.updateMultiple();
        
        var costBreakdowns = new GlideRecord("cost_plan_breakdown");
        costBreakdowns.addQuery("task", demandId);
        costBreakdowns.setValue('task', projectId);
        costBreakdowns.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        costBreakdowns.setWorkflow(false);
        costBreakdowns.updateMultiple();
        
        var fundingRecs = new GlideRecord("project_funding");
        fundingRecs.addQuery("task", demandId);
        fundingRecs.setValue('task', projectId);
        fundingRecs.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        fundingRecs.setWorkflow(false);
        fundingRecs.updateMultiple();
        
        this.updateBenefitPlans(demandId, projectId);

        //Update estimated and budget costs
        new PlannedTaskEntityUpdater().updatePlannedTaskEstimatedCost(project);
        new PPMTaskEntityUpdater().updateBudgetCost(project);
    },

    _copyFinancialFieldsFromDemandToProject:function(demand, projectId, projectTable){
        var project = new GlideRecord(projectTable);
        if ( project.get(projectId)) {
            project.discount_rate = demand.getValue("discount_rate");
            project.npv_value = demand.getValue("npv_value");
            project.irr_value = demand.getValue("irr_value");
            project.setWorkflow(false);
            project.update();
        }
    },

    updateBenefitPlans: function (demandId, projectId) {
        gs.print("Into updateBenefitPlans -> " + demandId + " | " + projectId);
        var project = new GlideRecord('pm_project');
        project.get(projectId);
        
        var benefitPlan = new GlideRecord("benefit_plan");
        benefitPlan.addQuery("task", demandId);
        benefitPlan.setValue('task', projectId);
        benefitPlan.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        benefitPlan.setWorkflow(false);
        benefitPlan.updateMultiple();

        var benefitBreakdowns = new GlideRecord("benefit_plan_breakdown");
        benefitBreakdowns.addQuery("task", demandId);
        benefitBreakdowns.setValue('task', projectId);
        benefitBreakdowns.setValue('sys_domain', project.sys_domain);
        benefitBreakdowns.setWorkflow(false);
        benefitBreakdowns.updateMultiple();
    },

    type: 'DemandToProjectCreationHelper'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>Michael.Ocasio@hhs.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-08-14 15:37:44</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>b89d4ee3dbb79b006bb976740f9619c7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>13</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DemandToProjectCreationHelper</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_b89d4ee3dbb79b006bb976740f9619c7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Keith.Tucker@hhs.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-08-15 15:26:47</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
